bzh.plealog.bioinfo.filter.implem

Class BFilterImplem

  • java.lang.Object
    • bzh.plealog.bioinfo.filter.implem.BFilterImplem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BFilter, Cloneable

    public class BFilterImplem
extends Object
implements BFilter
    This is a default implementation of interface BFilter. For internal use only. It contains a gateway between the high level Filter API and the underlying low-level Hyper-Graph Explorer (HGE) implementation that really does the filtering job.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
